data.description: Step inside and you will first notice the vaulted ceiling in the living room with chair railing and fireplace that adds beautiful character.  Home has a spacious kitchen with dinning area and a window over the sink so you can look out to the backyard & pool. The Owner suite has a large walk-in closet, private bath with separate shower, soaking tub and beautiful tray ceiling in the bedroom.  Owner suite also has access to the patio outside where you can enjoy cool nights and beautiful SC weather. 4 spacious bedrooms all downstairs and a large bonus room upstairs. This home is located in the perfect spot on a cul-de-sac and just a couple of minutes to the town of Elgin. Large back yard has plenty of space as well as an above ground Blue World Pool to cool of on those hot summer days! Short drive to Ft. Jackson military base and Columbia including the Sandhill Shopping area.  Just down the road from baseball fields, parks and the Elgin Veterans park.
